Basic Statistics

This is based off of this tutorial: https://speciationgenomics.github.io/filtering_vcfs/

library(tidyverse)

Variant quality

var_qual <- read_delim("data/vcftools_stats/hc-pools_thinned/hc-pools_thinned_CCGP-squid_stats.lqual", 
                       delim = "\t", 
                       col_names = c("chr", "pos", 
                                     "qual"), 
                       skip = 1, 
                       show_col_types = FALSE)

ggplot(var_qual,
       aes(qual)) +
  geom_density(fill = "thistle",
               colour = "black",
               alpha = 0.3) +
  xlim(0,5000) +
  theme_light()


summary(var_qual$qual)
     Min.   1st Qu.    Median      Mean   3rd Qu. 
    36.75   1644.18   2828.82   5886.52   6925.02 
     Max. 
131949.00 
quantile(var_qual$qual, 
         probs = c(0.05, 0.95))
        5%        95% 
  720.3205 22789.9900

Variant Depth

var_depth <- read_delim("data/vcftools_stats/hc-pools_thinned/hc-pools_thinned_CCGP-squid_stats.ldepth.mean", 
                        delim = "\t", 
                        col_names = c("chr", "pos", 
                                      "mean_depth", 
                                      "var_depth"), 
                        skip = 1, 
                        show_col_types = FALSE)

ggplot(data = var_depth, 
       aes(x = mean_depth)) +
  geom_density(fill = "thistle", 
               colour = "black", 
               alpha = 0.3) +
  xlim(0, 25) +
  theme_light()


summary(var_depth$mean_depth)
     Min.   1st Qu.    Median      Mean   3rd Qu. 
  0.03704   5.23585   6.63889   6.27995   7.57944 
     Max.

         probs = c(0.05, 0.95))

Variant Missingness

var_miss <- read_delim("data/vcftools_stats/hc-pools_thinned/hc-pools_thinned_CCGP-squid_stats.lmiss",
                       delim = "\t",
                       col_names = c("chr", "pos",
                                     "nchr", "nfiltered",
                                     "nmiss", "fmiss"),
                       skip = 1, 
                       show_col_types = FALSE)

ggplot(var_miss,
       aes(fmiss)) +
  geom_density(fill = "thistle",
               colour = "black",
               alpha = 0.3) +
  theme_light()


summary(var_miss$fmiss)

Minor Allele Frequency

var_freq <- read_delim("data/vcftools_stats/hc-pools_thinned/hc-pools_thinned_CCGP-squid_stats.frq",
                       delim = "\t",
                       col_names = c("chr", "pos",
                                     "nalleles", "nchr",
                                     "a1", "a2"),
                       skip = 1)
Rows: 535142 Columns: 6 Column specification 
Delimiter: "\t"
chr (1): chr
dbl (5): pos, nalleles, nchr, a1, a2
 Use `spec()` to retrieve the full column specification for this data.
 Specify the column types or set `show_col_types = FALSE` to quiet this message.
var_freq$maf <- var_freq %>%
  select(a1, a2) %>%
  apply(1, function(z) min(z))

ggplot(data = var_freq,
       aes(x = maf)) +
  geom_density(fill = "thistle",
               colour = "black",
               alpha = 0.3) +
  theme_light()
